{"tid":1658156,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【施政報告】首置客買800萬以下樓 可九成按揭 毋須過壓測 政府：絕非救市","createTime":"2019-10-16T11:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T13:06:42.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c31b5ad7d08c5f06169c511e157664275a4ab816","tid":1658156,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:58:48.000Z","msg":"政府消息人士：絕非救市<br />\n<br />\n政府消息人士指，最近樓市交投降溫，按揭證券公司認為是合適時間放寬按保，但強調「絕非救市」，初衷是協助因按保上限而延遲置業的中產及年輕人上車。<br />\n<br />\n對於會否進一步刺激樓價，他指樓價受多種因素因素影響，「按證唔認為單一政策就能夠影響樓價發展」，九成按揭樓價上限提升至800萬後，認為已經能夠涵蓋一般置業者需求。<br />\n<br />\n雖然按保放寬，但他指金管局仍會維持「風險為本」的原則，銀行壓力測試未有改變，「人工仍然要供得起先可以上車」。因為上限提高，按保保費亦會隨着風險因素增加，業主需要就額外貸款額繳交額外15%保費，但可以隨每月按揭還款攤分。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191016/60159175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191016%2F60159175&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9SryzeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=c2c1afc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191016%2F60159175&h=02085277\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191016/60159175</a>"},{"pid":"0d09d42b6c37d4447f965fa1efd8588dd624b235","tid":1658156,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f249edc1eee2c31e0a7f8b3064418a9929e81746","tid":1658156,"uid":8219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:11:24.000Z","msg":"邊到講無壓測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f891cfa8d7ba779a2af02556d2ae9afc765b01","tid":1658156,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:06:42.000Z","msg":"個個瘋狂借錢買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" clas